graph TD
    A([New Metric Window — 30 min]) --> B[Error Rate Collector]
    A --> C[Alert Frequency Counter]
    A --> D[Incident Duration Tracker]
    A --> E[Anomaly Count Collector]

    B --> F[Z-Score Normaliser\nmu and sigma from 30-day history]
    C --> F
    D --> F
    E --> F

    F --> G[Weighted Average\nScore 0 to 100]

    G --> H{Score band?}
    H -- "80 or above" --> I[Healthy]
    H -- "50 to 79"   --> J[Degraded]
    H -- "below 50"   --> K[Critical]

    I --> L[AI Executive Digest Panel]
    J --> L
    K --> L
